{
  "stem": "18572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 538.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The teacher was very, very nice, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She always took extra time out and would sit with me with children's books and teach me English.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember there was a rabbi also who was very nice, and he put me into Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So while everybody was trying to learn Hebrew-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Knowing the Hebrew, learning the English through the Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I learned very quickly, because by the following year, when I entered junior high school, I remember thinking-- I was hoping that I would already, you know, sound American.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could speak, but I couldn't, you know-- I still had the accent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had my braids-- I cut off my braids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got rid of the earrings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But everything was so strange, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came here, and they introduced me to someone in the family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a-- a-- a young girl who was my age, Ruth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're still friends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was playing with Barbie dolls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had never had a doll.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I might have had one at the age of four, before the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But here I'd gone through all of this, and like, with Barbie dolls was just-- you know, it was like coming to Mars or something for me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was always different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I really want it to be the same as everybody else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think by high school, I probably started fitting in a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Long Island City High School.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, as an aside-- this is sort of interesting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was in junior high school, I made friends with this boy who-- whose mother was a widow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we became very good friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
